<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #51545E;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-content {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #3869D4;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #FFFFFF;
    }
    .email-header img.logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .banner {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    p {
      margin: .4em 0;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 12px 15px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEC;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #F9FAFB;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .product-img {
      width: 60px;
      height: auto;
      vertical-align: middle;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #A8AAAF;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-content">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="email-header">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <img
          src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x50?text=Glimmer+Logo"
          alt="Glimmer Logo"
          class="logo"
        />
        <!-- Banner -->
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/600/200"
          alt="Store Banner"
          class="banner"
        />
        <h1>Thank you for your order, <%= customer.name %>!</h1>
        <p>Order #<%= order.id %> &bull; Placed on <%= order.date %></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <%= customer.name %>,</p>
        <p>We’re processing your order and will let you know once it ships. Below is a summary of what you purchased:</p>

        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Item</th>
              <th>Qty</th>
              <th>Price</th>
              <th>Total</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% order.items.forEach(item => { %>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="<%= item.image %>" alt="<%= item.name %>" class="product-img" />
                  <span><%= item.name %></span>
                </td>
                <td><%= item.quantity %></td>
                <td>PKR <%= item.price.toFixed(2) %></td>
                <td>PKR <%= (item.price * item.quantity).toFixed(2) %></td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
          </tbody>
          <tfoot>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" style="text-align: right; font-weight: bold;">Subtotal:</td>
              <td>PKR <%= order.subtotal.toFixed(2) %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" style="text-align: right; font-weight: bold;">Shipping:</td>
              <td>PKR <%= order.shipping.toFixed(2) %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" style="text-align: right; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Total:</td>
              <td style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">PKR <%= order.total.toFixed(2) %></td>
            </tr>
          </tfoot>
        </table>

        <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email or reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@glimmer.com.pk">support@glimmer.com.pk</a>.</p>
        <p>Thanks for shopping with us!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Glimmer. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

